Class CgiRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.attivio.sdk.esb.AbstractPlatformMessage
      • com.attivio.sdk.esb.CgiRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PlatformMessage, Serializable, Cloneable

    public class CgiRequest
extends AbstractPlatformMessage
    Message that represents a request via CGI on a HTTP receiver. Contains CGI parameters and HTTP headers.

      • create

        public static CgiRequest create(QueryRequest qreq)
        Creates a CgiRequest from a QueryRequest. This is the inverse operation of the QueryRequest create method. Not all queries and filters are guaranteed to have equivalent parseable string representations; this method cannot guarantee an equivalent CGI Request for such cases.
